Aim: write a program to implement various string operations

Algorithm: 
step1: start the program.
step2: intialize a string variable. 
step3: performed operations are in , not in, reversee, split function, find function , replace function, index function , lower & uppercase function concadenate.
step4: run the code.
step5: stop the program.

PROGRAM CODE:

print("string function")
str = "jain university"

print(" in and not in: ")
print("i" in str)
print("I"not in str)

print(" split function: ")
print(str.split())
print(str.split('i'))

print("find function:")
print(str.find("s"))

print("replace function:")
print(str.replace('j','J'))

print("index function:")
test = "this is a text messaage"
i=test.index("is")
print(i)

print("upper and lower funtion:")
print(str.upper())
print(str.lower())

print(" concadenate function:")
str1 = " is my collage "
concate = str+str1
print(concate)

print("reverse:")
s=str[::-1]
print(s)


